        private static <T extends KittyModel,E extends KittyMapper> java.util.Map<java.lang.Class<T>,java.lang.Class<E>> generateRegistryFromRegistryPairsAnnotationArray(KITTY_DATABASE_REGISTRY registryAnnotation)
        Returns map of registry classes generated from KITTY_DATABASE_REGISTRY.domainPairs() array. If any of model or mapper classes not regular implementations of KittyMapper or KittyModel than IllegalArgumentException would bw thrown.
        Also IllegalArgumentException would be thrown if KITTY_DATABASE_REGISTRY.domainPairs() length is zerolength
